# Web UI Rules

- Prioritize premium aesthetic designs (dark mode, glassmorphism, glowing accents).
- Keep CSS clean and well-structured, grouped by component.
- Do not use TailwindCSS unless explicitly requested; rely on Vanilla CSS.
- Ensure all DOM manipulations and Three.js logic are well-commented and optimized for performance (minimize main-thread blocking).
- Follow modern JavaScript best practices (ES6+).
